      <section eId="sec_1214">
        <num>1214</num>
        <heading>Application by attorney-general for removal of receiver and to close receivership</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_1214__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Whenever he deems it to be to the advantage of the shareholders,\ncreditors or other persons interested in the assets of any corporation\nfor which a receiver has been appointed, the attorney-general may move:\n</p>
          </content>
          <paragraph eId="sec_1214__subsec_a__subsec_1">
            <num>(1)</num>
            <content>
              <p>For an order removing the receiver and appointing another in his\nstead;\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_1214__subsec_a__subsec_2">
            <num>(2)</num>
            <content>
              <p>To compel the receiver to account;\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_1214__subsec_a__subsec_3">
            <num>(3)</num>
            <content>
              <p>For such other and additional orders as may facilitate the closing\nof the receivership.\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
        </subsection>
      </section>
